1113
01:22:33,416 --> 01:22:35,215
Tụi nó sẽ quay lại.

1114
01:22:52,133 --> 01:22:54,001
Oh!

1115
01:22:54,003 --> 01:22:55,536
Đi nào!

1116
01:22:55,538 --> 01:22:57,705
