1285
01:37:13,361 --> 01:37:15,094
Tránh phải lông bông thôi.

1286
01:37:15,096 --> 01:37:17,263
Khó mà kiếm được việc
khi có tiền sử trọng tội mà.

1287
01:37:17,265 --> 01:37:18,398
Yeah.

1288
01:37:18,400 --> 01:37:20,166
Nhưng tao buồn lắm.

1289
01:37:20,168 --> 01:37:24,838
Nghe này, tao có vài thứ.

1290
01:37:24,840 --> 01:37:28,041
Tao luôn cần những thằng như mày.

1291
01:37:28,043 --> 01:37:30,443
CHỉ cần mày muốn thôi.

1292
01:37:30,445 --> 01:37:31,611
MÀy có xe đi vào cuối tuần không

1293
01:37:31,613 --> 01:37:33,146
vào cuối tuần không

1294
01:37:33,148 --> 01:37:34,380
Không.

1295
01:37:34,382 --> 01:37:36,249
Tao đang cố tận dụng thờ gian.

1296
01:37:36,251 --> 01:37:38,885
Làm những việc tốt.

1297
01:37:38,887 --> 01:37:40,253
Oh, okay.

1298
01:37:40,255 --> 01:37:42,989
Không thể giúp
những thằng không muốn được giúp.

1299
01:37:42,991 --> 01:37:45,091
Chúc mày may mắn

1300
01:37:45,093 --> 01:37:46,459
với $7.50 đô một giờ.

1301
01:37:46,461 --> 01:37:48,628
Cứ gọi tao nếu cần.

1302
01:39:40,441 --> 01:39:42,175
MÀy là thằng L` nào?

1303
01:39:42,177 --> 01:39:43,409
Tao là James.

1304
01:39:43,411 --> 01:39:44,677
Sahra có đây không.

1305
01:39:44,679 --> 01:39:47,680
Tôi muốn gặp cô ấy.

1306
01:39:47,682 --> 01:39:50,283
Cô ấy không còn ở đây nữa.

1307
01:40:17,012 --> 01:40:19,178
Em đđính hôn rồi à.

1308
01:40:20,681 --> 01:40:21,514
Yeah.

1309
01:40:21,516 --> 01:40:22,515
Jake.

1310
01:40:22,517 --> 01:40:23,683
Anh ta làm gì?

1311
01:40:23,685 --> 01:40:25,585
Uh, dọn rác.

1312
01:40:25,587 --> 01:40:27,387
Anh ấy là người tốt.

1313
01:40:27,389 --> 01:40:30,390
Em thấy hạnh phúc.

1314
01:40:30,392 --> 01:40:32,525
Yeah.

1315
01:40:33,460 --> 01:40:35,661
Em xin lỗi vì đã không đến thăm.

1316
01:40:37,264 --> 01:40:40,466
Em đúng.

1317
01:40:40,468 --> 01:40:43,036
Tiếp tục sống.

1318
01:40:43,038 --> 01:40:44,504
Ở đó tệ lắm không?

1319
01:40:44,506 --> 01:40:46,539
Ổn cả rồi.

1320
01:40:47,808 --> 01:40:50,176
Em phải tìm ai đó yêu em...

1321
01:40:51,478 --> 01:40:54,247
và giữ...

1322
01:40:54,249 --> 01:40:55,415
James.

1323
01:40:55,417 --> 01:40:57,583
Aanh đã viết thơ.

1324
01:41:01,455 --> 01:41:02,755
Anh đi bất cứ đâu trong thành phố

1325
01:41:02,757 --> 01:41:06,325
và cảm thấy có thứ gì đó

1326
01:41:06,327 --> 01:41:07,493
kéo mình lại
1332
01:41:07,495 --> 01:41:09,662
với cuộc sống của chính anh.

1327
01:41:11,231 --> 01:41:13,566
CÒn khó hơn anh nghĩ.

1328
01:41:15,769 --> 01:41:19,472
Và chúng ta phải đi.

1329
01:41:19,474 --> 01:41:21,240
Đi đâu?

1330
01:41:21,242 --> 01:41:23,242
Xa

1331
01:41:24,378 --> 01:41:26,579
Thật xa.

1332
01:41:27,548 --> 01:41:30,249
New York.

1333
01:41:30,251 --> 01:41:31,684
Anh không biết.

1334
01:41:31,686 --> 01:41:34,454
anh không du tiền đến
New York, nhưng...

1335
01:41:34,456 --> 01:41:36,255
James?

1336
01:41:36,257 --> 01:41:38,224
Yeah?

1337
01:41:38,226 --> 01:41:40,326
đọc cho em 1 bài thơ đi.

1338
01:41:40,328 --> 01:41:43,329
Đi mà?

1339
01:41:43,331 --> 01:41:45,331
Okay.

1340
01:41:48,502 --> 01:41:52,238
In my mind, there's a boy
who exists in chains.
(Đoạn này là thơ nên xin phép không dịch)

1341
01:41:53,574 --> 01:41:56,742
Inside a cold, dark room
of painful solitude

1342
01:41:56,744 --> 01:41:59,378
is where he will remain.

1343
01:41:59,380 --> 01:42:03,182
Behind these walls
the sorrow is inevitable,

1344
01:42:03,184 --> 01:42:06,686
as relentless as
the passage of time.

1345
01:42:06,688 --> 01:42:09,388
Mentalities corrupt and dark,

1346
01:42:09,390 --> 01:42:10,723
brainwashed,

1347
01:42:10,725 --> 01:42:12,892
and hopelessly
blind.

1348
01:42:14,595 --> 01:42:17,263
Prisons are packed
with crowded spaces,

1349
01:42:17,265 --> 01:42:20,700
lifers and guards with
hollow faces.

1350
01:42:20,702 --> 01:42:23,336
Shackled hearts
afraid of changes,

1351
01:42:23,338 --> 01:42:26,506
and weakened wills
become complacent.

1352
01:42:26,508 --> 01:42:29,709
Yet, I maintain with patience,

1353
01:42:29,711 --> 01:42:33,479
time can limit
but not shatter my will,

1354
01:42:33,481 --> 01:42:35,148
strength blazed across my chest

1355
01:42:35,150 --> 01:42:37,817
as solid as
penitentiary steel.

1356
01:42:37,819 --> 01:42:39,785
But the silence speaks,

1357
01:42:39,787 --> 01:42:42,421
it tells me all I need to hear,

1358
01:42:42,423 --> 01:42:46,859
it confirms my beliefs and its
promises I have to fear.

1359
01:42:46,861 --> 01:42:51,297
It reminds me that without
freedom, I'm alone.

1360
01:42:51,299 --> 01:42:54,600
And these whitewashed walls
don't make up

1361
01:42:54,602 --> 01:42:57,637
for blackened souls.

1362
01:42:57,639 --> 01:43:02,308
I've given 95% of my boys
a handshake than a pound,

1363
01:43:02,310 --> 01:43:05,344
before they were either locked
down or buried off

1364
01:43:05,346 --> 01:43:07,647
in cemetery grounds.

1365
01:43:07,649 --> 01:43:12,351
What I've done is who I am,
but who I am is what I do now.

1366
01:43:12,353 --> 01:43:14,353
I won't let up or cease
to fight.

1367
01:43:14,355 --> 01:43:18,658
Just time,
I plan on doing it right.

1368
01:43:18,660 --> 01:43:22,828
And what's right
lies within me.

1369
01:43:22,830 --> 01:43:26,199
I'm learning to
appreciate my struggle

1370
01:43:26,201 --> 01:43:27,733
for it would be hard to find

1371
01:43:27,735 --> 01:43:30,670
the joy of accomplishment
without it.

1372
01:43:33,808 --> 01:43:35,908
We live and we learn.

1373
01:43:35,910 --> 01:43:39,312
We rise and we fall.

1374
01:43:39,314 --> 01:43:42,548
Like the heartbeat
of a sleeping giant,

1375
01:43:42,550 --> 01:43:44,817
with bittersweet dreams.

1376
01:43:44,819 --> 01:43:47,353
Stay up, never down.

